      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WAIKARE ADRIENNA (2) looks close to a win having come from tougher barriers to place in her last three outings, last week leading from wider for third at this venue. Up a little in grade but can take advantage of the low draw. WITH APLOMB (11) broke last start but was racing well prior, recording three wins and two placings from her previous six starts. With manners and even luck from a tricky barrier she is a player. CHARLIES TACTICS (4) has had seven weeks off but has been kept up to the mark by placing in two trials. Drew wide and worked when midfield last time and recorded a string of placings prior. Has to come into calculations. KARBINE (6) resumes after four months. Was tackling the good three-year-olds at the end of last campaign but recorded a string of wins and placings earlier. Proven fresh so keep safe.",
